                    <note>Taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="EMML7281">EMML (HMML) 7281, f. 32v</ref>.</note>
                    <ab> ወሀለወት፡ አሐቲ፡ ብእሲት፡ ዘታፈቅር፡ ገይሠ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን። በበዓለ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ በ፪ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ወእንዘ፡ ተሐውር፡ በፍኖት፡ ደክመት፡ ወአጽለለት፡ በታሕተ፡ ኦም። ወመጽኡ፡ ኀቤሃ፡ መላእክተ፡ ሰማይ። ወተከሉ፡ ደብተራ፡ ወሐይመተ።</ab>
                </div>
            </div><!--  
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <note>Translated by Jeremy Brown, edited by Wendy Laura Belcher, Jeremy Brown, Mehari Worku & Dawit Muluneh <ref type="mss" corresp="EMML7281">EMML (HMML) 7281, f. 32v, in 2022.</note>
             <ab>A miracle performed by Our Lady Mary, the Holy Two-fold Virgin, Mother of God.
A woman loved to journey to the church on the feast of Our Lady Mary, the Holy Two-fold Virgin, Mother of God. But [one time] while traveling, she grew weary and took shelter beneath a tree.
[Suddenly] heavenly angels came to her and set up a tent and a tabernacle. Then they administered to her the body and the blood of her creator, the Son.
May her prayers and her blessings be with us and with her servant Walda Maryam, forever and amen, amen.</ab>
